#: /Users/alalji/Downloads/splunk/etc/apps/splunk-monitoring-console/default/checklist.conf:300
msgid "Check individual machines to identify the source of the excessive memory usage with the Monitoring Console Resource Usage: Machine or Resource Usage: Instance pages."
